        <para> If you select your "Home" folder, you see that two new buttons appear in the line above the folder hierarchy. </para>
        <para> One of them allows you to create a folder inside a folder that belongs to you or that is shared with you 
            <graphic fileref="images/folder_add.png" align="center" valign="middle"/>&#160;. 
            </para>
        <para>
            <graphic fileref="images/walk-through.11.1.png" align="center" valign="middle"/>
        </para>
        <para> If you select a folder which is bold, a dialogue window appears in which you can give a name to the folder you want to create. 
            You can use any characters you wish in the folder name, including spaces.</para>
        <para>
            <graphic fileref="images/walk-through.11.2.png" align="center" valign="middle"/>
        </para>
